"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-adam-peaty-exclusive-interview-paris-olympics-swimming-b1172332.html\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the search feature\", \"from\": 7, \"to\": 25}, {\"ngram\": \"your consent\", \"from\": 35, \"to\": 47}, {\"ngram\": \"cookies\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 99}, {\"ngram\": \"similar technologies\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"search\", \"from\": 175, \"to\": 181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our privacy policy\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 205}, {\"ngram\": \"more information\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics IfAdam Peatywas looking for a sign, there it was, screaming back at him.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 317, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sport|Olympics\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 243}, {\"ngram\": \"IfAdam\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 250}, {\"ngram\": \"a sign\", \"from\": 272, \"to\": 278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sliding into the pew at the Nottingham church where he now returns every Sunday, that first time a little lost and looking for answers, the sermon that day was all about theOlympic Games.\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 346, \"end\": 356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nottingham\", \"score\": 0.9999999977549123, \"rank\": 1.800970585023634e-09, \"text\": \"Nottingham\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nottingham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nottingham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pew\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 338}, {\"ngram\": \"answers\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 452}, {\"ngram\": \"the sermon\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 464}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympic Games\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"No one knew I was coming,\\\" he recalls of what has proved a seminal moment.\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 582, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No one\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 514}, {\"ngram\": \"a seminal moment\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was just at the back and I was like, 'if this is not meant for me, then what is?'\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 667, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the back\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not think society has the answers I am seeking, especially as a young man, and it's nothing to do with being an athlete.\\\"\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 794, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"society\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"the answers\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 706}, {\"ngram\": \"a young man\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 746}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 764}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For almost the entirety of his career, he had the answers when it came to being the quickest breaststroke swimmer of all time: of how to win on the big days; the Olympic golds; the world titles; and yet there was still a void in his life.\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 1034, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"almost the entirety\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 819}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 833}, {\"ngram\": \"the answers\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"the quickest breaststroke swimmer\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 909}, {\"ngram\": \"all time\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 921}, {\"ngram\": \"the big days\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic golds\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 971}, {\"ngram\": \"the world titles\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 989}, {\"ngram\": \"a void\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1033}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has talked of the battle he has faced and come out the other side of as \\\"three years of hell\\\", a time in which he sunk into depression and became reliant on alcohol.\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1204, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the battle\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1063}, {\"ngram\": \"the other side\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1104}, {\"ngram\": \"three years\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1123}, {\"ngram\": \"hell\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1131}, {\"ngram\": \"depression\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"alcohol\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1203}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Steadily, he has begun to find himself, although he readily admits: \\\"It's still very hard and it's still changing slowly.\\\"\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1327, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The origin of his turnaround began in Melbourne, where he was introduced to Pastor Ashley Null, a currently Berlin-based clergyman who works with a number of elite swimmers.\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1367, \"end\": 1376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9999994725314109, \"rank\": 5.270668815268019e-07, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 1412, \"end\": 1418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashley_Abbott\", \"score\": 0.9983426515790644, \"rank\": 0.0016589909119509372, \"text\": \"Ashley\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashley_Abbott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashley_Abbott\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The origin\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1339}, {\"ngram\": \"his turnaround\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1357}, {\"ngram\": \"a currently Berlin-based clergyman\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1459}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1483}, {\"ngram\": \"elite swimmers\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When back in Europe, the pair met up in Nottingham.\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1543, \"end\": 1553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nottingham\", \"score\": 0.9999999977549123, \"rank\": 1.800970585023634e-09, \"text\": \"Nottingham\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nottingham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nottingham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1522}, {\"ngram\": \"the pair\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty then witnessed his poignant first sermon and, as he puts it, \\\"I have been there ever since\\\".\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1653, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1560}, {\"ngram\": \"his poignant first sermon\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1601}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At theParis Olympics, his faith will be abundantly clear, as people tune in to watch his attempt to seal a hat-trick of 100metre breaststroke titles.\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1804, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theParis Olympics\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"his faith\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1686}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1722}, {\"ngram\": \"his attempt\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1751}, {\"ngram\": \"a hat-trick\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1771}, {\"ngram\": \"100metre breaststroke titles\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On his torso is a large cross with the words 'Into the Light' inked beneath it.\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his torso\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1817}, {\"ngram\": \"a large cross\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1834}, {\"ngram\": \"the words\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1849}, {\"ngram\": \"the Light\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1865}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are others he credits with his turnaround beyond the religious overhaul.\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1964, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1902}, {\"ngram\": \"his turnaround\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1933}, {\"ngram\": \"the religious overhaul\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 1963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is his coach, Mel Marshall, who effectively threw him back in the water, warning that the clock was ticking to Paris.\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 2088, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2082, \"end\": 2087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6083045047952894e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his coach\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 1983}, {\"ngram\": \"Mel Marshall\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 1997}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2042}, {\"ngram\": \"the clock\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then there is his girlfriend, Holly Ramsay, daughter of the celebrity chef Gordon, who has himself been a big support behind the scenes.\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2124, \"end\": 2129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holly_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9998931736747048, \"rank\": 0.00010675809199376121, \"text\": \"Holly\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holly_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holly_Cunningham\"}, {\"begin\": 2130, \"end\": 2136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Ramsay\", \"score\": 0.999987113473521, \"rank\": 1.2886423000272577e-05, \"text\": \"Ramsay\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Ramsay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Ramsay\"}, {\"begin\": 2169, \"end\": 2175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Gordon\", \"score\": 0.9984954901585736, \"rank\": 0.0015067655435233214, \"text\": \"Gordon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Gordon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Gordon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his girlfriend\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2122}, {\"ngram\": \"daughter\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2146}, {\"ngram\": \"a big support\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2211}, {\"ngram\": \"the scenes\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2229}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The biggest thing Mel did was get me back in the water six or eight weeks after I stopped, just to literally paddle,\\\" he recalls.\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2362, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The biggest thing\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2250}, {\"ngram\": \"Mel\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2254}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2278, \"to\": 2287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She said, 'If you want to do this at the Olympics next year, you have got to just start feeling the water now'.\\\"\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2476, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2413}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was baby steps, or strokes, at first, finding his way back physically and mentally before ramping up the training at home and in Thailand before racing in Doha and finally London, where he returned to the times of old at April's Olympic trials.\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2610, \"end\": 2618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5475543060476038, \"rank\": 0.8262827177391209, \"text\": \"Thailand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2636, \"end\": 2640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0426679073517824e-18, \"text\": \"Doha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"baby steps\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2495}, {\"ngram\": \"strokes\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2507}, {\"ngram\": \"his way\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2534}, {\"ngram\": \"the training\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2594}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2602}, {\"ngram\": \"the times\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2691}, {\"ngram\": \"April's Olympic trials\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is something about Mel,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2745}, {\"ngram\": \"Mel\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's extremely charismatic and extremely tough.\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2816, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Holly Ramsay posts father Gordon Ramsay's reaction to her on wedding day Adam Peaty's family 'give up hope of reconciliation after Ramsay's wedding comment' Aquatics GB 'immensely disappointed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games Discover a hidden island paradise in the Indian Ocean \\\"You never want to lose that tough side, because you have got to make it in this sport, especially for a third Olympics.\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 3220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2892, \"end\": 2902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 2950, \"end\": 2956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Ramsay\", \"score\": 0.999987113473521, \"rank\": 1.2886423000272577e-05, \"text\": \"Ramsay\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Ramsay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Ramsay\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Holly Ramsay posts\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2836}, {\"ngram\": \"wedding day\", \"from\": 2879, \"to\": 2890}, {\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2924}, {\"ngram\": \"reconciliation\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2942}, {\"ngram\": \"Aquatics GB\", \"from\": 2975, \"to\": 2986}, {\"ngram\": \"Proud\", \"from\": 3015, \"to\": 3020}, {\"ngram\": \"Enhanced Games Discover\", \"from\": 3027, \"to\": 3050}, {\"ngram\": \"a hidden island paradise\", \"from\": 3051, \"to\": 3075}, {\"ngram\": \"the Indian Ocean\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3095}, {\"ngram\": \"that tough side\", \"from\": 3120, \"to\": 3135}, {\"ngram\": \"this sport\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3182}, {\"ngram\": \"a third Olympics\", \"from\": 3199, \"to\": 3215}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have got to be asking questions, like 'how can we get faster?'\", \"from\": 3221, \"to\": 3287, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 3247, \"to\": 3256}]}, {\"sentence\": \"but ignore all the other stuff, because that's irrelevant.\", \"from\": 3288, \"to\": 3346, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the other stuff\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not care what other people are doing.\\\"\", \"from\": 3347, \"to\": 3390, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other people\", \"from\": 3366, \"to\": 3378}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is not entirely true.\", \"from\": 3392, \"to\": 3418, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One of his major rivals for gold in Paris, Qin Haiyang, was among 23 Chinese swimmers caught up in a contamination case for the substance TMZ, for which they were cleared of any wrongdoing.\", \"from\": 3419, \"to\": 3608, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3455, \"end\": 3460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6083045047952894e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3462, \"end\": 3473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Haiyang\", \"score\": 0.9999938624998401, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Qin Haiyang\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Haiyang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Haiyang\"}, {\"begin\": 3488, \"end\": 3495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9380189138867819, \"rank\": 0.06215094655235858, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his major rivals\", \"from\": 3426, \"to\": 3442}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 3447, \"to\": 3451}, {\"ngram\": \"a contamination case\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3538}, {\"ngram\": \"the substance TMZ\", \"from\": 3543, \"to\": 3560}, {\"ngram\": \"any wrongdoing\", \"from\": 3593, \"to\": 3607}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty is not here to talk of the rights and wrongs of that, but is frustrated with the World Anti-Doping Agency's handling of the case.\", \"from\": 3610, \"to\": 3745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3697, \"end\": 3721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World Anti-Doping Agency\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 3610, \"to\": 3615}, {\"ngram\": \"the rights\", \"from\": 3639, \"to\": 3649}, {\"ngram\": \"wrongs\", \"from\": 3654, \"to\": 3660}, {\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 3736, \"to\": 3744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As an athlete, we all want to be treated fairly and with transparency\\\"; the hope being that any doping \\\"results are not hidden and put under secrecy\\\".\", \"from\": 3747, \"to\": 3898, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 3751, \"to\": 3761}, {\"ngram\": \"transparency\", \"from\": 3805, \"to\": 3817}, {\"ngram\": \"the hope\", \"from\": 3820, \"to\": 3828}, {\"ngram\": \"any doping \\\"results\", \"from\": 3840, \"to\": 3859}, {\"ngram\": \"secrecy\", \"from\": 3889, \"to\": 3896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He, like many of his peers he says, \\\"are very disappointed in WADA\\\".\", \"from\": 3899, \"to\": 3967, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his peers\", \"from\": 3916, \"to\": 3925}, {\"ngram\": \"WADA\", \"from\": 3961, \"to\": 3965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that brings the issue of the hat-trick of Olympic titles to add to golds in his individual event in Rio de Janeiro and Tokyo.\", \"from\": 3969, \"to\": 4098, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4073, \"end\": 4087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5456245616183518e-17, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 4092, \"end\": 4097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9997781988346589, \"rank\": 0.0002218445473591121, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the issue\", \"from\": 3985, \"to\": 3994}, {\"ngram\": \"the hat-trick\", \"from\": 3998, \"to\": 4011}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic titles\", \"from\": 4015, \"to\": 4029}, {\"ngram\": \"golds\", \"from\": 4040, \"to\": 4045}, {\"ngram\": \"his individual event\", \"from\": 4049, \"to\": 4069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It gives me goosebumps any time I think of it,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 4100, \"to\": 4157, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"goosebumps\", \"from\": 4113, \"to\": 4123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I can not get carried away with too much thought.\", \"from\": 4158, \"to\": 4212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"too much thought\", \"from\": 4195, \"to\": 4211}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not many people have done that, be dominant in the same event at three Olympics in a row.\", \"from\": 4213, \"to\": 4302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Not many people\", \"from\": 4213, \"to\": 4228}, {\"ngram\": \"the same event\", \"from\": 4260, \"to\": 4274}, {\"ngram\": \"three Olympics\", \"from\": 4278, \"to\": 4292}, {\"ngram\": \"a row\", \"from\": 4296, \"to\": 4301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have got to make sure I keep my emotions in check.\\\"\", \"from\": 4303, \"to\": 4356, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my emotions\", \"from\": 4334, \"to\": 4345}, {\"ngram\": \"check\", \"from\": 4349, \"to\": 4354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That said, he has talked in the past of \\\"swimmingangry\\\", that particular emotion getting the best out of him at key moments in his career.\", \"from\": 4358, \"to\": 4496, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 4386, \"to\": 4394}, {\"ngram\": \"that particular emotion\", \"from\": 4415, \"to\": 4438}, {\"ngram\": \"key moments\", \"from\": 4470, \"to\": 4481}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 4485, \"to\": 4495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He expects that anger to bubble up come Paris, too.\", \"from\": 4497, \"to\": 4548, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4537, \"end\": 4542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6083045047952894e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that anger\", \"from\": 4508, \"to\": 4518}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he does feel a different athlete and person to the one who triumphed at the Covid Games in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 4549, \"to\": 4650, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4644, \"end\": 4649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9997781988346589, \"rank\": 0.0002218445473591121, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a different athlete\", \"from\": 4566, \"to\": 4585}, {\"ngram\": \"person\", \"from\": 4590, \"to\": 4596}, {\"ngram\": \"the one\", \"from\": 4600, \"to\": 4607}, {\"ngram\": \"the Covid Games\", \"from\": 4625, \"to\": 4640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There, I really relied on my ego to get the job done,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 4652, \"to\": 4716, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my ego\", \"from\": 4679, \"to\": 4685}, {\"ngram\": \"the job\", \"from\": 4693, \"to\": 4700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I thought, 'I am the best, so I should perform the best'.\", \"from\": 4717, \"to\": 4775, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now my belief system is a multitude of things.\", \"from\": 4776, \"to\": 4822, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my belief system\", \"from\": 4780, \"to\": 4796}, {\"ngram\": \"a multitude\", \"from\": 4800, \"to\": 4811}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 4815, \"to\": 4821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am almost a new person through various ways.\\\"\", \"from\": 4823, \"to\": 4870, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new person\", \"from\": 4835, \"to\": 4847}, {\"ngram\": \"various ways\", \"from\": 4856, \"to\": 4868}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the metamorphosis, he hopes the result is the same.\", \"from\": 4872, \"to\": 4931, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the metamorphosis\", \"from\": 4880, \"to\": 4897}, {\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 4908, \"to\": 4918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I used to rely on my ego to get the job done... now I am almost a new person Adam Peaty As for what lies beyond Paris, at this stage he has no idea, so blinkered has his vision been towards his main event.\", \"from\": 4933, \"to\": 5140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5011, \"end\": 5021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 5047, \"end\": 5052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6083045047952894e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my ego\", \"from\": 4951, \"to\": 4957}, {\"ngram\": \"the job\", \"from\": 4965, \"to\": 4972}, {\"ngram\": \"a new person\", \"from\": 4997, \"to\": 5009}, {\"ngram\": \"this stage\", \"from\": 5055, \"to\": 5065}, {\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 5073, \"to\": 5080}, {\"ngram\": \"his vision\", \"from\": 5099, \"to\": 5109}, {\"ngram\": \"his main event\", \"from\": 5123, \"to\": 5137}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He says the next Games, in Los Angeles, by which time he will be 33, will be a target if he is still fast enough and still has the motivation.\", \"from\": 5141, \"to\": 5283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5168, \"end\": 5179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 1.0550476549166196e-11, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the next Games\", \"from\": 5149, \"to\": 5163}, {\"ngram\": \"which time\", \"from\": 5184, \"to\": 5194}, {\"ngram\": \"a target\", \"from\": 5218, \"to\": 5226}, {\"ngram\": \"the motivation\", \"from\": 5268, \"to\": 5282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And occasionally his mind wanders to the bad times possibly returning.\", \"from\": 5285, \"to\": 5355, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his mind\", \"from\": 5302, \"to\": 5310}, {\"ngram\": \"the bad times\", \"from\": 5322, \"to\": 5335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time around, he feels he has the support network to not spiral out of control in the same way.\", \"from\": 5356, \"to\": 5455, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the support network\", \"from\": 5390, \"to\": 5409}, {\"ngram\": \"control\", \"from\": 5431, \"to\": 5438}, {\"ngram\": \"the same way\", \"from\": 5442, \"to\": 5454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have definitely got the structure, but I do not know what's ahead of me,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 5457, \"to\": 5542, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the structure\", \"from\": 5480, \"to\": 5493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Some of the most evil stuff could still be ahead of me, some of the stuff that breaks people.\", \"from\": 5543, \"to\": 5637, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most evil stuff\", \"from\": 5552, \"to\": 5571}, {\"ngram\": \"the stuff\", \"from\": 5608, \"to\": 5617}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5630, \"to\": 5636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It would be very naive of me to say I have a structure in place and it's going to fix everything.\", \"from\": 5639, \"to\": 5737, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a structure\", \"from\": 5683, \"to\": 5694}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 5698, \"to\": 5703}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 5726, \"to\": 5736}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We know the world is a very unpredictable place.\", \"from\": 5738, \"to\": 5786, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 5746, \"to\": 5755}, {\"ngram\": \"a very unpredictable place\", \"from\": 5759, \"to\": 5785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All we can do is prepare and, hopefully, smile in the face of adversity.\\\"\", \"from\": 5787, \"to\": 5860, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 5837, \"to\": 5845}, {\"ngram\": \"adversity\", \"from\": 5849, \"to\": 5858}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the water, Peaty was always about predictability, with the quick times and the gold medals.\", \"from\": 5862, \"to\": 5956, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 5865, \"to\": 5874}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 5876, \"to\": 5881}, {\"ngram\": \"predictability\", \"from\": 5899, \"to\": 5913}, {\"ngram\": \"the quick times\", \"from\": 5920, \"to\": 5935}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medals\", \"from\": 5940, \"to\": 5955}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Paris, he aims to repeat that.\", \"from\": 5957, \"to\": 5990, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5960, \"end\": 5965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6083045047952894e-13, \"text